    "content": "Bad Romance\r\ntabbed by bass50611\r\nHaving looked at the other bass tabs, some don't fit and\r\nsome are so long (one tab 6 pages of A4!)\r\nI was getting dizzy just trying to\r\nwork them out so here is my simplified version.\r\nMakes the song so much easier to play and it does fit.\r\n\r\n[tab]Intro:             (QUAVERS)\r\nG|------------|-----------------------------------------|\r\nD|---NO BASS--|-----------------------------------------|\r\nA|-FIRST PART-|---------------------00000000-33333333---|\r\nE|------------|---11111111-33333333---------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse 1: First Part no bass\r\n\r\n[tab]Part 2:\r\nG|--------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-----2-2-3-2------2-2-3-2-----2-2-3-2-------------|\r\nA|-0-0----------0-0---------0-0---------3-3-3---3-3-|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Part 3:       (PLAY THIS x4)\r\nG|--------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-00000000---3333-------00000000---3333------|\r\nE|-----------------3333------------------3333-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus/Refrain:                         (QUAVERS ~ PLAY THIS x2)\r\nG|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-33333333-55555555-77777777------0-2-------------------------------------|\r\nA|---------------------------3333-3---3---------------------------33333333-|\r\nE|--------------------------------------11111111-33333333-55555555---------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nRepeat Part 2 of Verse\r\n\r\nRepeat Part 3 of Verse:\r\n\r\nRepeat Chorus/Refrain:\r\n\r\nRepeat Part 2 of Verse x2:\r\n\r\n[tab]Bridge:           (PLAY THIS BIT x2)\r\nG|---------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------|\r\nA|-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3-|\r\nE|---------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-3--------5--------7-------------------3---------5---------7----------|\r\nA|-----------------------------3--------------------------------------3-|\r\nE|----------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|-1--------3--------5---------8---------1-----------3---------5--------x-|[/tab]\r\n\r\nRepeat Chorus/Refrain:\r\n\r\nOutro: Same As Part 2 of verse ~ No Bass",
    "is_backing_track_under_review": false,
    "is_tab_ml": false
